title: Sykesville man accused of possessing, sharing files of child pornography - The Baltimore Sun
text:
Jacob Alan Gunther, 34, of the 7500 block of Gaither Road, is charged with one count each of promoting and distributing child pornography and possession of child pornography, according to electronic court files. Gunther was released Monday from the Carroll County Detention Center on $30,000 bail, according to electronic court files.
 The Baltimore Sun.
